# LAMMPS Input File
# Licensed under CC BY 4.0
# A Set of Materials-Science Tutorials for the LAMMPS Simulation Package: 2. Materials Science
# By Simon Gravelle, Mark A. Tschopp, Jacob R. Gissinger, and Axel Kohlmeyer
# Tutorial 18: 1. Bulk rutile TiO2 with the COMB charge-transfer potential
#
# Build the rutile TiO2 crystal with lattice custom, equilibrate the atomic
# charges self-consistently with fix qeq/comb, and relax the tetragonal cell
# to zero stress.  The relaxed lattice constants and the EFFECTIVE charges
# (compare with the formal Ti(4+) and O(2-)) are reported at the end.

# 1) Initialization
units metal
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style charge

# 2) System definition
# rutile TiO2: space group P4_2/mnm, a = 4.5937, c = 2.9587, u = 0.3048
# (experimental values); 6-atom conventional cell: 2 Ti + 4 O
lattice custom 1.0     a1 4.5937 0.0 0.0  a2 0.0 4.5937 0.0  a3 0.0 0.0 2.9587     basis 0.0    0.0    0.0     basis 0.5    0.5    0.5     basis 0.3048 0.3048 0.0     basis 0.6952 0.6952 0.0     basis 0.8048 0.1952 0.5     basis 0.1952 0.8048 0.5
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 4.5937 4.5937 2.9587
region box block 0 3 0 3 0 4
create_box 2 box
Created orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (13.7811 13.7811 11.8348)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms 1 box basis 1 1 basis 2 1 basis 3 2 basis 4 2 basis 5 2 basis 6 2
Created 216 atoms
  using lattice units in orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (13.7811 13.7811 11.8348)
  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds
mass 1 47.867
mass 2 15.999

# 3) Settings
# starting charges: any neutral guess works, qeq re-equilibrates them
set type 1 charge  2.4
Setting atom values ...
  72 settings made for charge
set type 2 charge -1.2
Setting atom values ...
  144 settings made for charge
pair_style comb
pair_coeff * * ffield.comb Ti O
Reading comb potential file ffield.comb with DATE: 2011-02-22
neighbor 0.5 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
# re-equilibrate the charges at every step of the minimization
fix q all qeq/comb 1 0.0001

# 4) Monitoring: average charge per element alongside the thermo output
group ti type 1
72 atoms in group ti
group ox type 2
144 atoms in group ox
compute qti ti property/atom q
compute qavti ti reduce ave c_qti
compute qox ox property/atom q
compute qavox ox reduce ave c_qox
thermo 25
thermo_style custom step pe press lx lz c_qavti c_qavox

# 5) Relax the cell (a and c independently) and the atoms
fix relax all box/relax aniso 0.0 vmax 0.001
min_style cg
min_modify dmax 0.005 line quadratic
minimize 1.0e-10 1.0e-10 2000 10000
